Can't believe it's working!

39:36.245 --> 39:37.945
Yeah!

39:37.947 --> 39:39.347
Nice!

39:39.349 --> 39:41.983
Good job!

39:41.985 --> 39:43.719
Kari: I can't believe that worked!

39:43.721 --> 39:45.087
Tory: The rear spear!

39:45.089 --> 39:46.556
Dude, that's awesome!

